title: Hour 2 - Kareem Abdul Jabbar (06-02-20)

description:
Kareem Abdul Jabbar tell Dan about the first time he met Muhammad Ali on Sunset Avenue during his Freshman year at UCLA. Kareem says he was walking down Sunset and saw Ali on the sidewalk entertaining some people while doing magic tricks.
